---
import { LUGAR_MAPA } from '@/consts/links'
---

<section id="venue" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-t from-dark-bg to-[#111]">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-js-yellow uppercase tracking-[2px] font-bold mb-2">LA SEDE</h4>
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold font-display mb-5 text-white">La Nave, Madrid</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-5 leading-relaxed">
          Un antiguo espacio industrial transformado en el centro de innovación más importante de la
          ciudad. Techos altos, luz natural y una acústica increíble para una experiencia
          inolvidable.
        </p>
        <div class="mb-8">
          <div class="flex gap-4 mb-4">
            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt text-js-yellow mt-1"></i>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-white block">Dirección</strong>
              <span class="text-gray-400">C. Cifuentes, 5, Villaverde, 28021 Madrid</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <i class="fas fa-subway text-js-yellow mt-1"></i>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-white block">Metro</strong>
              <span class="text-gray-400">Villaverde Bajo-Cruce (Línea 3)</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a
          href={LUGAR_MAPA}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3.5 font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-sm bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white rounded hover:bg-white hover:text-js-black transition-all"
        >
          Ver en Google Maps
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="rounded-[20px] overflow-hidden h-[300px] lg:h-[400px] border-2 border-white/10 shadow-2xl relative group"
      >
        <img
          src="/la-nave.webp"
          alt="La Nave Madrid"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
        />
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
